{"tid":1534942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九七入機場唔係唔得，一定要有策略同後路","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:34:33.000Z","uid":135867,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"21cac0dee140ab0287e0fe415bda97e56873376d","tid":1534942,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:23:57.000Z","msg":"其實都講左好多次唔洗真係入機場<br />\n同埋不如畀前線抖返一日<br />\n上次入去塞住<br />\n跟住後面啲想來支援嘅巴打入唔到來<br />\n<br />\n不如傾下實際行動係點先<br />\n如果唔係得個宣傳<br />\n大家去到嗰日都唔知做乜<br />\n<br />\n專心谷文宣咁：果幾位巴打可唔可以谷埋行動細節<br />\n如果唔係畀你叫曬啲人去又係送頭"},{"pid":"c3f6d273f3151814a650b9171ba78df9e9d170bb","tid":1534942,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c13b45f04011a3cef036c0242fdd8f8b15717e02","tid":1534942,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"機場係春袋<br />\n去其他地方 無效果同作用"},{"pid":"7e30be794f734fa801404dc544cac517306056d1","tid":1534942,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"36407cb099c9422217f87e8bb515d99e43efb8f9","tid":1534942,"uid":198175,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"和理非主場, 唔帶gear, 連black bloc都唔駛, 有車坐車, 有鐵坐鐵, 有隊排隊."},{"pid":"9d28dc6d582a041ac1a5fc8f04a8d40de577fbbd","tid":1534942,"uid":108337,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"實際行動就係搭車同揸車<br />\n唔好咁傻成日覺得要&quot;做啲野&quot;先叫有意義，實際係自己打飛機拎光環，害撚死人"},{"pid":"76a950753e6d19f090db1d25db2914778a644e67","tid":1534942,"uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c13b45f04011a3cef036c0242fdd8f8b15717e02","tid":1534942,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"機場係春袋<br />\n去其他地方 無效果同作用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"我認同<br />\n但係上一次你都見到<br />\n入咗去之後好難出返嚟<br />\n<br />\n講真我哋上次行路出去<br />\n佢有心捉就拉曬㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n之前講好咗淨係塞<br />\n又話循環出入機場<br />\n都好似冇乜人做咁 <br />\n跟住又有人set road block<br />\n<br />\n機場真係險地來 所以要做就一定要有計劃<br />\n<br />\n你同我都知冇可能幾十萬人一齊入去㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n咁不如討論下要點做好過"},{"pid":"e3684061c56054750a81b9e9f061b7b2ceda95bd","tid":1534942,"uid":76609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"冇GEAR 就唔怕 CHECK"},{"pid":"a8c44d73bbf339d6a9da0b84fe6e9d301867f75b","tid":1534942,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"喺東涌集合一次過行入去機場有冇得諗"},{"pid":"5c8e4f8fa422c7fdda893e15a65b458564d85801","tid":1534942,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9565a0b3a1e266fb5b95a1754b96db13b7e235d4","tid":1534942,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:33:39.000Z","msg":"同埋其實你都入唔到terminal㗎喇"},{"pid":"174d05d6d276d38208dbd866ace0aaa1c5751067","tid":1534942,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc